#Hierarchical Inheritance: 💻
✅Hierarchical Inheritance is a type of inheritance where one parent class is inherited by 
multiple child classes.

🐍Syntax:
class Parent:
 # statement block
class Child1(Parent):
 # statement block
class Child2(Parent):
 # statement block
class Child3(Parent):
 # statement block

